{
  "texts": [
    "We conduct an adversarial evaluation leveraging two widely-used benchmark datasets: MaliciousInstruct [24] and AdvBench [4].",
    "We generate adversarial suffixes for each prompt in these datasets using a total of four generative attack models: two variants of AmpleGCG and two variants of AmpleGCG-plus [3,22].",
    "We use HarmBench [25] as a measure of whether the model's response to an prompt-suffix pair constitutes a jailbreak.",
    "Table 1: Defense pipeline results on the Malicious Instruct [24] and AdvBench [4] datasets.",
    "We use k = 20 beams for generating the adversarial suffixes due to memory constraints."
  ]
}